If you have something to say, say it.

27
00:03:39,777 --> 00:03:42,287
I wanted to ask you something.

28
00:03:44,073 --> 00:03:46,542
If I ever saw you again,

29
00:03:47,493 --> 00:03:49,270
I wanted to ask you.

30
