00:18:00,788 --> 00:18:02,623
Jungo!

213
00:18:09,510 --> 00:18:12,970
 Tokyo, 5 years ago 

214
00:18:15,512 --> 00:18:17,996
What's up with him?

215
00:18:19,057 --> 00:18:21,550
I heard he got dumped.

216
00:18:22,835 --> 00:18:26,564
What are you looking at me for? I dumped him ages ago.

217
00:18:26,564 --> 00:18:28,090
Right?

218
00:18:28,090 --> 00:18:30,636
I wondered if you two had got back together.

219
00:18:30,636 --> 00:18:34,447
Some people get back together after breaking up.

220
00:18:34,447 --> 00:18:36,758
He has been popular lately.

221
00:18:36,758 --> 00:18:39,202
Is that why he has no time to write?

222
00:18:39,202 --> 00:18:44,874
Here I am, writing every day, and I barely get anything done.

223
00:18:44,874 --> 00:18:47,685
But he's out getting girls all the time.

224
00:18:47,685 --> 00:18:50,647
- I wonder if he gets any time to write.
 - Right.

225
00:18:50,647 --> 00:18:54,551
What's the point of writing quality stuff?

226
00:18:54,551 --> 00:18:57,377
I want to have some romance, too.

227
00:19:19,768 --> 00:19:22,419
Can I have one?

228
00:19:40,204 --> 00:19:42,416
I do feel a bit upset.

229
00:19:42,416 --> 00:19:47,495
You didn't have such a hard time when we broke up.

230
00:19:47,495 --> 00:19:49,189
I haven't broken up yet.

231
00:19:49,189 --> 00:19:52,699
Is that how she sees it, though?

232
00:19:52,699 --> 00:19:57,363
If you really miss her that much, shouldn't you try

233
00:19:57,363 --> 00:19:58,781
something to get her back?

234
00:19:58,781 --> 00:20:01,784
What do you know?

235
00:20:01,784 --> 00:20:04,037
I know enough.

236
00:20:04,037 --> 00:20:07,957
I know you probably haven't contacted her,

237
00:20:07,957 --> 00:20:11,793
although you miss her like crazy.

238
00:20:19,611 --> 00:20:21,345
Jungo.

239
00:20:24,365 --> 00:20:26,758
If you're having such a hard time...

240
00:20:29,595 --> 00:20:32,022
why don't we get back together?

241
00:20:37,530 --> 00:20:39,940
 Seoul, today 

242
00:20:40,857 --> 00:20:43,651
I thought you were busy.

243
00:20:43,651 --> 00:20:46,195
You're the star of our company.

244
00:20:46,195 --> 00:20:48,389
I was worried knowing you're here all by yourself.

245
00:20:48,389 --> 00:20:52,852
And the promotion in Korea is pretty important for the company, too.

246
00:20:52,852 --> 00:20:57,065
Everyone's taking really good care of me here.

247
00:20:57,065 --> 00:20:59,116
You've got nothing to worry about.

248
00:20:59,116 --> 00:21:00,693
I know, but still.

249
00:21:00,693 --> 00:21:05,715
I thought you'd be really happy to see me if I showed up like this.

250
00:21:05,715 --> 00:21:08,809
Can't you at least act as if you're happy to see me?

251
00:21:09,369 --> 00:21:11,270
I am happy.

252
00:21:13,034 --> 00:21:15,704
I'm leaving on Tuesday for Fukuoka anyway

253
00:21:15,704 --> 00:21:18,022
to meet Mr. Kudo.

254
00:21:18,920 --> 00:21:22,172
So, I'll keep you company until then.

255
00:21:23,633 --> 00:21:25,510
Thanks.

256
00:21:25,510 --> 00:21:29,389
